parameters: You can gather the necessary materials to craft accessories and other items.
Give the crafted items to the girls to increase their affection points.
To save the declining elf village and the World Tree,
have sex with the elf girls and make babies!
There are no game overs or time limits, so
please enjoy a carefree and leisurely impregnation slow life.
By having sex with the girls and giving them presents,
you can increase the intimacy level through communication.
When the intimacy level and number of births meet certain conditions, the intimacy level will rise,
and the implantation rate will increase or new events will occur.
Once you become intimate with a girl, you can even marry her,
so actively approach them and raise the intimacy level.
The number of elves has decreased, and the World Tree has weakened.
Make babies with the girls to increase the number of babies and restore the World Tree's health.
The implantation rate during baby-making is affected by the girl's intimacy level and menstrual cycle.
Get along with the girls and aim for the dangerous days to increase the chances of implantation.
When the World Tree recovers, crop yields will increase,
and there will be various other benefits, so keep making babies and having them give birth.
The number of elves has decreased, and the village has declined.
You can develop the village by donating money.
Money can be earned by shipping crops grown in the fields,
or by selling items you've obtained, such as fish and ores.
As the village develops, more facilities will be added, and you'll be able to expand your house,
so there will be more new things you can do, so keep donating!
